title: HSGameTime Scoreboard: Monday, October 12
text:
10:48 p.m. GIRLS GOLF
BIG VIII LEAGUE
Norco 220, Roosevelt 251 at Goose Creek GC. Low scores — Gragnolati (N) 40, Hardister (R) 44.
GIRLS TENNIS
NONLEAGUE
King 12, Riverside Poly 6. Doubles sweeps — S. Desar-F. DeMicco (K), B. Patel-T. Elliott (K).
(King is 13-2, 6-0 in league. Poly is 13-2m 6-0.)
GIRLS VOLLEYBALL
BG VIII LEAGUE
Norco def. Centennial, 25-13, 25-17, 25-20. Kills — Frew (N) 14, Edwards (C) 10. Digs — Frew 11, Edwards 11.
(Norco is 14-5, 4-0 in league. Centennial is 6-13, 0-4.)
Santiago def. Roosevelt, 25-13, 25-10, 25-18. Kills — Morohunfola (R) 6, Wolfe (S) 13, Turang (S) 13, Shollin (S) 10. Digs — Smevog (S) 19.
(Santiago is 24-3, 4-0 in league. Roosevelt is 17-5, 2-2.)
CITRUS BELT LEAGUE
Yucaipa def. Redlands East Valley, 25-19, 25-27, 26-24, 21-25, 15-10. Kills — Walley (Y) 14, Hadder (Y) 13, Fisher (Y) 11. DIgs — Hadder (Y) 18, Walley (Y) 12, Scina (Y) 15.
